The '''2005 Monaco Grand Prix Formula Three''' was a support race for the [[2005 Monaco Grand Prix]] held on the [[Circuit de Monaco]] in [[Monte Carlo]]. It was the first time Formula Three cars had raced at Monaco since 1997, and remains the last to date. The race was the fourth round of [[2005 Formula Three Euroseries season|2005]] [[Formula Three Euroseries]]. The first race was held on May 20, and the second race held on the May 21.
