'''Ahmed Yusuf Yasin''' ({{lang-so|Axmed Yuusuf Yaasiin}}) (born  1957, [[Hargeisa]], [[Somaliland]] is a Somali Politician and Lawyer.
he was the [[Vice-President of Somaliland|Vice-President]] of [[Somaliland]], from 2002 until 2010 and he was the second chairman of UDUB party. he hails from the '''Adan Issa''' subdivisions of
[[Habar Awal|Issa Musse]] [[Isaaq]] [[Somalis]]. He was appointed as Vice President in 2002.<ref>https://books.google.com/books?id=Gk2QAgAAQBAJ</ref>

