'''Bosnia and Herzegovina''' participated in the '''Eurovision Song Contest 1996''' in [[Oslo]], Norway.  [[Amila Glamočak]] represented Bosnia and Herzegovina with the song "[[Za našu ljubav]]". They finished on 22nd place out of 23 countries with 13 points. It was the worst result for Bosnia and Herzegovina until {{Escyr|2016}}.

