[[Image:RO-Gendarmerie-OR1.png|thumb|right|The shoulder insignia of a ''Jandarm'']]

'''Jandarm''' (''Gendarme'') is the lowest rank in the [[Jandarmeria Română|Romanian Gendarmerie]]. It is the equivalent of [[Soldat (Romania)|soldat]] ({{lang-en|soldier}}) in the [[Romanian Armed Forces|Romanian Army]].

In day do day usage, the term ''jandarm'' denotes every man or woman enrolled into the [[Jandarmeria Română|Romanian Gendarmerie]], irrespective of their actual rank.

